'''''Fighter Within''''' is a fighting video game developed by Belgian studio [[Daoka]] and published by [[Ubisoft]]. It was released on November 22, 2013 as an exclusive [[Launch game|launch title]] for the [[Xbox One]].<ref>{{cite news |last= Scullion|first= Chris |date= August 20, 2013|title= Xbox One: Fighter Within trailer and screens|url= http://www.computerandvideogames.com/425348/xbox-one-fighter-within-trailer-and-screens/ |newspaper= |location= |publisher= Computerandvideogames|accessdate= November 10, 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last= Usher|first= William |date= August 20, 2013|title= New Gameplay Trailer Released For Xbox One's Fighter Within|url= http://www.cinemablend.com/games/Gameplay-Trailer-Released-Xbox-One-Fighter-Within-60136.html |newspaper= |location= |publisher= Cinema Blend LLC|accessdate= November 10, 2013}}</ref>
==Gameplay== {{Empty section|date=April 2017}}
==Reception== {{expand section|date=November 2013}} {{Video game reviews | MC = 23/100<ref name="metacritic" /> | EuroG = 1/10<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-11-29-fighter-within-review | title = Fighter Within review | publisher = Eurogamer | accessdate = 2013-11-29 | date = 2013-11-29 | first = Ellie | last = Gibson}}</ref> | GSpot = 2/10<ref>{{cite web|last=Walton |first=Mark |url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/fighter-within-review/1900-6415583/ |title=Fighter Within Review |publisher=GameSpot |date=2013-12-02 |accessdate=2016-09-20}}</ref> | IGN = 2.7/10<ref name="IGN" /> | rev1 = ''[[Hardcore Gamer]]'' | rev1Score = 1.5/5<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hardcoregamer.com/2013/11/24/review-fighter-within/63590/|title=Review: Fighter Within |work=[[Hardcore Gamer]]|publisher=Hardcore Gamer|first=Steve|last=Hannley|date=November 24, 2013|accessdate=November 25, 2013}}</ref> }} Fighter Within was panned by critics, and holds a Metacritic score of 23 out of 100, and [[List of video games notable for negative reception|became notable for its negative reception]].<ref name="metacritic">{{cite web | url = http://www.metacritic.com/game/xbox-one/fighter-within | title = Fighter Within for Xbox One Reviews | publisher = Metacritic | accessdate = 2013-11-29}}</ref> The Kinect controls were universally criticized, with several reviews suggesting problems were just as prevalent as the Kinect for Xbox 360. [[Game Informer]] gave the game a 1 out of 10, saying "Fighter Within is garbage." <ref name="IGN">{{cite web | url = http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/11/22/the-fighter-within-review | title = The Fighter Within Review | publisher = IGN}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.egmnow.com/articles/reviews/egm-review-fighter-within | title = EGM Review: Fighter Within | publisher = EGM}}</ref> GameZone's Mike Splechta gave Fighter Within a 2.5/10, stating "Fighter Within really showcases the larger problem with Kinect only games: they just don't work."<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamezone.com/reviews/2013/12/04/fighter-within-review-a-flailed-attempt|title=Fighter Within Review: A flailed attempt|last=Splechta|first=Mike|publisher=GZ|date=4 December 2013|accessdate=23 January 2014}}</ref>
