{{nihongo|'''Takayuki Haga'''|芳賀 隆之|Haga Takayuki|born January 26, 1955}}, better known by the stage name {{nihongo|'''George Tokoro'''|所ジョージ|Tokoro Jōji}}, is a Japanese comedian, TV personality, singer-songwriter, and essayist. Born in [[Tokorozawa, Saitama]], he attended [[Takushoku University]]'s Commercial Science class.{{cn|date=October 2016}}
